name: Experiment Or Die #74
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The Cybermen were my favorite robot nemesis but because of the single eye in todays design, i'm feeling Sentinel from X-Men as well. I'm seeing a fleshy cyclops, or a sunrise over a bunch of flamingos. Just gotta charge up. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
